high_descs: Walk forward to the bed, then turn left and walk across the room to the desk on the left of the bed.
Pick up the statue on the desk which is behind the mug.
Turn left and walk to the left side of the desk and stand to the left of the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a statue by the light of a desk lamp.

high_descs: Move a step forward then turn left. Turn right and face the desk on the left.
Pick up the statue from the right side of the desk.
Carry the statue and turn to the left just passed the desk.
Hold the statue and turn on the lamp on top of the desk.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a statue and turn on the lamp.

high_descs: Walk over to the bed, then hang a left and walk over to the right side of the wooden desk.
Pick up the rightmost statue off of the wooden desk.
Walk over to the left side of the wooden desk.
Turn on the small lamp that is on top of the wooden desk.
anns.task_desc: Examine a statue in the light of a small lamp.
